<header class="wks-header">
    <h1 class="wks-title wks-title--main">Game over</h1>
</header>
<section class="wks-text">
    {{#if highScore}}
        <p>
            You perished bravely in battle... AND got a new high score of {{score}} points!
        </p>
        <p>
            Tell us your name so it will live on through the ages in the high scores list!
        </p>
        <input
            type="text"
            id="nameInput"
            pattern=".{3,}"
            required
            placeholder="Enter your name..."
            class="wks-input"
        />
        <input
            type="submit"
            id="saveHighScore"
            value="Save"
            class="wks-submit"
        />
    {{else}}
        <p>
            You gave it your best. Alas, they gave it their best...er.
        </p>
        <p>
            Luckily you can try again as the available ships in our fleet
            are practically infinite! Strap yourself in and try again.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you were to achieve a high score, your name will live on
            through the ages in the high scores list!
        </p>
    {{/if}}
</section>
<footer class="wks-footer">
    <section class="wks-menu">
        <button class="wks-button wks-menu__play-button">Play</button>
        <button class="wks-button wks-menu__home-button">Home</button>
    </section>
</footer>
